DE_BSG_Galactica

-=20120401=-

By: G.o.d.W.a.n.4.


This map based on the Battlestar Galactica's series. The cylones in the fleet want to make a sabotage while the Cylone riders make an air strike.

Objectives:

	Terrorist (as Cylone):

		- Plant the bomb at A or B

		- Kill all Human people in the fleet

	Counter-Terrorist (as Galactica's fleet):

		- Kill all Cylone before they are planting the bomb

		- Defuse the bomb before it's exploding



Notes:

The map is basicly a DE map but i think it wont be fun without a very great team coz the narrow corridors and the good covers in the bombsites. So basicly it's a real tactical map and may repuered a stronger pc of the lights.
